text: Osorgino () is a rural locality (a village) in Taptykovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 238 as of 2010. There are 20 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Ufa, 5 km from Taptykovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Osorgino, Ufimsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
